text: Alphonse Nshimiyiama (born 1 July 1965) is a Rwandan former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Rwandan male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Rwanda Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
